            <div class="title">
                Protection Of Animals (Hunting And Coursing Prohibition) Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1949-02-25/debates/822c60d3-186b-4b83-9b82-f6f064fb9003/SwedishHousesScotland" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
