<p class="">This statement was made by a well-known writer in the "Sunday Pictorial," a paper with a large circulation, and if it were not true I suppose <span id="2172" class="column-number" data-column-number="2172"></span> some action could be taken or some denial could be made. I have not seen any denial made of that statement.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-70d21dc8-d181-4ec5-8df6-5dd62df448ff" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
