<p class="">Those are details which could be gone into at the time. I agree that a rifle would be best, but it would be dangerous for other people; shooting with buck shot is another way, and perhaps shooting with heavy revolvers, too.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
