<p class="">Does the hon. Member suggest arming them with machine guns?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-de99aae2-0b9e-4482-8311-67bbc1b5f05a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
