<p class="">I am glad to hear what the hon. Gentleman has said, but I hold in my hand this leaflet. I hope there will be a new and revised edition of it and that we shall be told the real reasons.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
