        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e762c0be-d144-427f-bf51-8ab95e2a931b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
