    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">In case there may be some misunderstanding, I should like to inform my hon. Friend that the Press officer of the Ministry of Agriculture does not write books for me or for the Ministry of Agriculture. He is a free person away from his duties and presumably he is quite entitled to write just what he likes.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ea4feb0d-d850-4fe4-b92b-b9eefab8f160" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-25/debates/f0f9debc-6257-43a7-a2d7-c7925868992f/ProtectionOfAnimals(HuntingAndCoursingProhibition)Bill#contribution-ea4feb0d-d850-4fe4-b92b-b9eefab8f160">
