                Mr. Paget
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2cb60e51-fe81-4b2a-b98c-33ddc83e88ff" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-25/debates/f0f9debc-6257-43a7-a2d7-c7925868992f/ProtectionOfAnimals(HuntingAndCoursingProhibition)Bill#contribution-2cb60e51-fe81-4b2a-b98c-33ddc83e88ff">
